results.content:
Overview:
American Pipelining Solutions (APS) is your long-term partner in trenchless pipe repair. We provide reliable tools, expert training, and real-world support to help contractors boost efficiency and profit—on every job, every day. With decades of combined industry experience, our team brings global trenchless innovations to the U.S. market—making them accessible, practical, and profitable for contractors across North America. APS offers industry-leading products like Raptor Cutter, Protect & Pull, Versa-Patch, Versa-Light, Houseliner, RIDGID, Dancutter, Sewertronics, Speedylight, Sacpro, and QuickSight. Whether you're patching, lining, inspecting, descaling, or locating leaks, we’ve got the gear and guidance to help you do it right. Our training programs are tailored to every level—from CIPP lining and UV curing to patching, descaling, and leak locating. We don’t just train—we stay with you long after the job starts, offering real-time technical support and jobsite troubleshooting when it matters most. Looking for a mobile solution? We design and build custom CIPP trucks and trailers, ranging from budget-friendly setups to premium rigs that maximize ROI and workflow. APS is also a certified repair center for cameras, cutters, jetters, and more—getting your tools back in the field and working like new. When you work with APS, you're not just buying equipment. You're gaining a partner that’s committed to your long-term success.
